Arik Air is giving its customers a real treat on Monday, February 14, 2022 which marks this year’s Valentine’s Day. According to the statement sent to The Ameh News and endorsed by Adebanji Ola, PR & Communications Manager in the company saying Passengers flying Arik Air on the day stand a chance to win complimentary hotel stay (for couples) in selected 5-star hotels in Lagos and Abuja. Additionally, a good number of free return tickets will be won via raffles on the day. Arik Air is embarking on the Valentine’s Day giveaways as a show of love for its esteemed guests who have supported and trusted the airline over the years. Advertisement Chief Executive Officer of Arik Air, Captain Roy Ilegbodu elaborated: “Valentine’s Day is now considered as an occasion to celebrate relationships. At Arik Air we value relationships and this is why we are giving our customers a treat on Valentine’s Day come Monday”. Intending passengers are advised to book their flights online at www.arikair.com or download the Arik mobile app on Google Play or Apps Store.  